25:[["$","blockquote",null,{"children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"阅读提示\n适合对象：想系统学习 Metasploit 模块、Payload 和会话管理的读者。\n阅读前提：知道漏洞利用、监听、反弹 Shell 等基础概念。\n核心收获：把从模块选择到会话利用的完整链路走通。\n说明：模块路径、兼容 payload 和漏洞利用成功率会随版本与目标环境变化。"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"Metasploit Framework 是全球使用最广泛的渗透测试框架，由 HD Moore 于 2003 年创建，如今由 Rapid7 公司维护。它将渗透测试的各个环节——信息收集、漏洞利用、后渗透、报告生成——整合在一个统一的平台中，极大地提高了渗透测试的效率。本文将从 Metasploit 的架构设计讲起，深入探讨其核心模块、实战利用流程、Meterpreter 会话管理以及自动化攻击技术，带你完整走通一次从扫描到 getshell 的渗透测试流程。"}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"metasploit-架构概览","children":["Metasploit 架构概览",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#metasploit-架构概览","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"Metasploit Framework 采用模块化架构，各组件各司其职："}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"核心模块类型","children":["核心模块类型",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#核心模块类型","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",["$","table",null,{"children":[["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","th",null,{"children":"模块类型"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"说明"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"示例路径"}]]}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Exploit"}]}],["$","td",null,{"children":"漏洞利用模块"}],["$","td",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"exploit/windows/smb/ms17_010_eternalblue"}]}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Payload"}]}],["$","td",null,{"children":"攻击载荷（反弹Shell等）"}],["$","td",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"payload/linux/x64/shell_reverse_tcp"}]}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Auxiliary"}]}],["$","td",null,{"children":"辅助模块（扫描、嗅探等）"}],["$","td",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"auxiliary/scanner/portscan/tcp"}]}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Post"}]}],["$","td",null,{"children":"后渗透模块"}],["$","td",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"post/linux/gather/hashdump"}]}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Encoder"}]}],["$","td",null,{"children":"编码器（绕过检测）"}],["$","td",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"encoder/x86/shikata_ga_nai"}]}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"NOP"}]}],["$","td",null,{"children":"NOP 滑板生成器"}],["$","td",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"nop/x86/opty2"}]}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Evasion"}]}],["$","td",null,{"children":"免杀模块"}],["$","td",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"children":"evasion/windows/windows_defender_exe"}]}]]}]]}]]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"payload-类型详解","children":["Payload 类型详解",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#payload-类型详解","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L2d","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"msfconsole-基本使用","children":["msfconsole 基本使用",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#msfconsole-基本使用","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"启动与核心命令","children":["启动与核心命令",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#启动与核心命令","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L2e","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"模块搜索技巧","children":["模块搜索技巧",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#模块搜索技巧","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L2f","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"信息收集模块实战","children":["信息收集模块实战",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#信息收集模块实战","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n"